extnewpage-field-title: Label of the namespace and title fields on the special page.
extnewpage-toolbox-label: Link label shown in the sidebar's toolbox.
accesskey-extnewpage:
{{ignored}}
Hotkey for Special:NewPage if in toolbox. Do not change if not needed.
extnewpage-help-nsheading: Informational heading in the page's right rail.
extnewpage-help-nstext: Informational text about namespaces in MediaWiki in the page's right rail.
extnewpage-help-contributeheading: Informational heading in the page's right rail.
extnewpage-help-contributetext: Text guiding towards further edits in the page's right rail, always shown.
extnewpage-help-contributetext-searchdig: Text guiding towards further edits of pages indicated in Extension:SearchDigest in the page's right rail. This is only shown if Extension:SearchDigest is installed.
extnewpage-newpagetext-fallback: Message shown below the title field, for a namespace without specialised text if title is correct.
extnewpage-newpagetext-0: Message shown below the title field, for main namespace if title is correct.
extnewpage-newpagetext-1: Message shown below the title field, for talk namespace if title is correct.
extnewpage-newpagetext-2: Message shown below the title field, for user namespace if title is correct.
extnewpage-newpagetext-3: Message shown below the title field, for user talk namespace if title is correct.
extnewpage-newpagetext-4: Message shown below the title field, for project namespace if title is correct.
extnewpage-newpagetext-5: Message shown below the title field, for project talk namespace if title is correct.
extnewpage-newpagetext-6: Message shown below the title field, for file namespace if title is correct.
extnewpage-newpagetext-8: Message shown below the title field, for MediaWiki namespace if title is correct.
extnewpage-newpagetext-10: Message shown below the title field, for template namespace if title is correct.
extnewpage-newpagetext-12: Message shown below the title field, for help namespace if title is correct.
extnewpage-newpagetext-14: Message shown below the title field, for category namespace if title is correct.
extnewpage-newpagetext-828: Message shown below the title field, for Scribunto/Module namespace if title is correct.
